          = @business.name
          |  in&nbsp;
          = @business.location.city_and_state
          |  is using Locable's web platform for local marketing, <strong>cross-promotion</strong>, & <strong>collaboration</strong> to help us <strong>#TakeBackLocal</strong>.
      tr
        td.padding-0 align="left" style="padding:0px 8px;font-family:'HelveticaNeue-Light','Helvetica Neue Light','Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#5D5D5D;line-height:22px;letter-spacing:0.03em;"
